posting_body: ['We have a ONE LEVEL two bedroom townhome in a beautiful, quiet neighborhood.', 'Medicine Lake is just minutes away from Minneapolis and St. Paul, with the famous Luce Line walking/biking trail directly connected to our property.', 'We consider it to be in a superb location!', "We are in the Wayzata school district, and we are a pet friendly community!Each unit has it's own washer and dryer!", '***', 'SNOW IS COMING BEFORE YOU KNOW IT!!', "YOU WON'T GET CAUGHT SHOVELING OUT YOUR CAR WITH OUR 2 CAR GARAGES!", '*', '**', 'Come check out our new Dog Park!', 'Renting for $1,895 avail August 15th!', ' Call The Office For More Details!', '  Pet Policy:Allow Cats, Dogs up to 80 Lbs., with Some Breed RestrictionsDeposit $100-$400Plus 1-time Pet Rent12 month leaseRENTAL FEATURES INCLUDE:', 'Dining room - Living room - Dishwasher - Dryer - Garbage disposal - Refrigerator - Stove/Oven - Washer - Private Patio - Pond - Air conditioning - Central A/C - Central heat - Double pane windows - Cable-ready - Guest parking - Garage - Detached - Off-street parking - On-street parkingFox Forest | Park Avenue of Wayzata |1798 Magnolia Ln N, Plymouth, <URL>Plymouth, Maple Grove, Minnetonka, Wayzata, Wayzata School District, Medicine Lake, Golden Valley, New Hope, 2 Bedroom Apartment, 3 Bedroom Apartment, Townhouse, Townhome, Town House, Town Home, Pet Friendly, Dogs Accepted, Cats Accepted, Garage, Two Story, Rental Home, Rental Apartments, House for Rent, Apartment for Rent!']
